OL,3,CInside Tehran as filmmaker secretly
OL,4,Crecords life during Iran war
OL,6,FOver the first ten days of war in
OL,7,FIran, an Iranian filmmaker has been
OL,8,Fsending us videos and voice notes
OL,9,Fdocumenting her perspective of the war
OL,10,Fin the capital, Tehran.
OL,12,FThis piece by ITV News and Zandland is
OL,13,Ftold in our filmmaker's voice, but we
OL,14,Fhave altered the sound with AI for her
OL,15,Fprotection. We are calling her Shirin.
OL,17,FIran's internet blackout is now in its
OL,18,F19th day and getting footage out of
OL,19,Fthe country has been extremely
OL,20,Fdifficult since the US and Israel
OL,21,Flaunched joint attacks on February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
