OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773876313
OL,3,CInside Tehran as filmmaker secretly
OL,4,Crecords life during Iran war
OL,6,FA filmmaker in Iran has been sending
OL,7,FITV News videos and voice notes
OL,8,Fdocumenting her perspective during the
OL,9,Ffirst ten days of the war in Tehran
OL,11,FOnly a chosen few have been given
OL,12,Faccess to the internet, while the rest
OL,13,Fof the country has little to no
OL,14,Fconnection under increasingly tight
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,FThose in Iran face not just the threat
OL,18,Fof bombs, but also persecution from
OL,19,Fthe regime. The videos were recorded
OL,20,Fat great risk - if caught, she could
OL,21,Fface the death penalty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
