OL,3,CInside Tehran as filmmaker secretly
OL,4,Crecords life during Iran war
OL,6,F"I think the people here, after
OL,7,Fenduring the protests, the harshness,
OL,8,Fthe crackdown, and then into a war...
OL,9,FI think it's absolutely heartbreaking,
OL,10,Fabsolutely heartbreaking, I think I
OL,11,Fcan just break down and cry right
OL,12,Fnow", Shirin says.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
